þyngdaraflsvandamálið.

482
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:43,473
Ég lofa því.

483
00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:57,679
Farðu.

484
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:09,595
Murph.

485
